name: Dystopia
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: Dystopia is a decentralized exchange and automated market marker focused on providing efficient token swaps and deep liquidity for stablecoins and other assets. Dystopia has a sophisticated governance structure using the ve(3,3) system that provides the possibility to maximize gains for all users of the ecosystem.
